name: SwiftCash
description: SwiftCash describes itself as an open-source, self-funded system of decentralized governance and economy born out of a desire to create a digital store of value with a consistent and stable growth model, as well as a peer-to-peer cryptocurrency for daily transactional use. SwiftCash uses a Proof-of-Stake algorithm to reach consensus and allows up to 70% of future block rewards to be spent on proposals that are supported by the community.
